text.tspan: Create something awesome at Syracuse University’s
A hackathon is an innovation marathon. You'll spend 24 hours working
with a team or by yourself to build an app, website, game, or any other
There will be prizes, food, networking, and coding workshops! You’ll get to
meet new people and learn new skills.
How do I find a team?
You can build a team beforehand, but there will also be team building
activities at the event. You can also work by yourself if you prefer.
College students in the CNY area (undergraduate AND graduate students
are both welcome). We do not plan on offering a remote option.
What if I want to sponsor CuseHacks?
CuseHacks is full of talented and passionate coders, developers,
engineers, and designers who would love to learn about your company
